content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Service Gateway Firmware Version 3.0.21 July 16, 2025—Service Gateway Firmware Version 3.0.21 includes enhancements, bug fixes, and security updates for Service Gateway. This update includes the following changes: This update enables customers to deploy the Service Gateway virtual appliance on Google Cloud Platform from Marketplace. This update provides more details on the ActiveUpdate Service status and shows a warning message on the console when pattern update fails. This update addresses various issues to improve overall system reliability and correctness. © 2025 Trend Micro Incorporated. All rights reserved.Search Knowledge Base
